microprocessor_definition.name: Fast Input & Output from Instrument Panel

object.n: Roll: Pos Hold Integral Clamp (MAX & MIN) (PID)
Pitch: Pos Hold Integral Clamp (MAX & MIN) (PID)

object.script:
--Debug View
function onTick() roll = input.getNumber(1) pitch = input.getNumber(2) collective = input.getNumber(3)
FL = input.getNumber(4) FR = input.getNumber(5) RL = input.getNumber(6) RR = input.getNumber(7)
end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(255,255,0)
screen.drawText(0,0,"Rol: "..("%.2f"):format(roll)) screen.drawText(0,10,"Pit: "..("%.2f"):format(pitch)) screen.drawText(0,20,"Col: "..("%.2f"):format(collective))
screen.drawText(0,35,"FL: "..("%.2f"):format(FL)) screen.drawText(0,45,"FR: "..("%.2f"):format(FR)) screen.drawText(0,55,"RL: "..("%.2f"):format(RL)) screen.drawText(0,65,"RR: "..("%.2f"):format(RR))
end
